{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1710446, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "作为文科生表示人体内一半氮元素是工业合成的？有点可怕", "timestamp": 1621763286, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710450, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得这些都属于ky。倒不如说喂饱世界最多人的是太阳呢", "timestamp": 1621763319, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: ？氮元素怎么合成啊", "timestamp": 1621763338, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710452, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: “元素”是工业合成的，这句话说法是不对的。", "timestamp": 1621763344, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710454, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "工业合成的是物质，只是利用了元素。", "timestamp": 1621763363, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710455, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 满足当代农业的氨必须得合成，但工业合成≠可怕", "timestamp": 1621763370, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710457, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "又没人说哈伯的不好 合成氨确实是人类最伟大的创造之一 但是到这里来ky干啥呢", "timestamp": 1621763380, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710459, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 而且你这个氮元素也不是合成的", "timestamp": 1621763393, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710460, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "我也可以说世界上很多的氧元素来自于恐龙喝过的水。", "timestamp": 1621763400, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710461, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710457, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 确实，大家不如感谢太阳", "timestamp": 1621763410, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710542, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不对吧，文章说的是氮元素来自合成氨路线，并不是说合成氮元素吧", "timestamp": 1621764416, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710555, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "文章说的合成氨对农业的巨大意义没错，但是去比谁养活更多的人就是抬杠。", "timestamp": 1621764586, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz啊，这段话的意思是人体内50%的氮元素的来源（也就是食物）要归功于合成氨技术的发明。因为有合成氨才有了更多的化肥，人才能种出更多的粮食。这些化肥中的氮元素进入人体，所以说氮元素来源于合成氨，并不是说人合成了氮元素。具体参考图片。\n另外，这个人举哈伯的例子真是没意思，哈伯在一战时给德国造了很多化学武器，间接杀死了上百万人。", "timestamp": 1621765743, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710641, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 237, "w": 435}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710446, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1621765755, "type": "image", "url": "j4/j43ej5ktcaztpjznb6j3t3w6d6j3f2ac.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1710654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": 1710641, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 确实，哈伯是一个非常有争议的化学家\n另外，dz的理解应该是有一点偏差，你可以理解为“人工合成”指的是将氮元素从空气中的氮气转化为可以被生物利用的氮元素化合物的过程，这个成果是非常重要的", "timestamp": 1621765922, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1710867, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 336391, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哈伯是少数几个虽然历史上就是负面人物但我还是愿意认定他是伟人的人。\n但是现在这个时间点说不就是KY怪嘛。。。\n\n（话说合成氮不是高中化学知识吗？", "timestamp": 1621768329, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1411, "w": 994}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 336391, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1621763220, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1621768329, "url": "gd/gdgi2p2w6hdjnjtypxpozrsq4nu7vv7z.jpeg", "vote": {}}}